        public static List<Object> simpleOrPersistablePathToPathItemsOrNull(String path)
        Parameters:
        path - path str to parse
        Returns:
        list of path items in case the provided path
        • is simple (e.g. "/dicomConfigurationRoot/globalConfiguration/dcmTransferCapabilities" )
        • is persistable (e.g. "/dicomConfigurationRoot/dicomDevicesRoot[@name='someName']")

        otherwise null
